direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# ── Column 1: Entry ──────────────────────────────────
entry: |md
  **/konflux-build-simulator**

  [repository-url]
  Simulates Konflux build
  environment on PRs
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# ── Column 2: Repo Analysis ─────────────────────────
clone: |md
  **Clone & Scan**

  Shallow clone repo
  Read Dockerfiles
  Read package.json
  Detect build args
|

detect: |md
  **Detect Repo Type**

  Monorepo (turbo.json)
  Operator (CRDs)
  Component/Library
  Module Federation
|

# ── Column 3: Phase 0 Static Checks ─────────────────
lockfile: |md
  **Hermetic Lockfile**

  npm: git+/github:/file:
  go.sum existence
  go mod verify
  Resolved URL check
|

workspace: |md
  **Workspace Deps**

  Detect scope & dirs
  Cross-ref COPY cmds
  Runtime vs dev deps
  Missing package warn
|

fips: |md
  **FIPS Compliance**

  esbuild removal
  strictfipsruntime tag
  Go binary flags
  Release blocker warn
|

preflight: |md
  **Hermetic Preflight**

  docker --network=none
  npm ci --ignore-scripts
  Root + module lockfiles
  <1 min validation
|

# ── Column 4: Phase 1-2 Build & Runtime ──────────────
docker-build: |md
  **Docker Build**

  Production BUILD_MODE
  Multi-stage build
  COPY path validation
  Build arg injection
|

runtime: |md
  **Runtime Validation**

  Container startup
  Crashloop detection
  Health check wait
  Log error scan
|

api-test: |md
  **API Endpoint Tests**

  merge-patch+json (415)
  json-patch+json (415)
  Fastify v5 regression
  28+ operations check
|

ws-test: |md
  **WebSocket Tests**

  Connection crash detect
  @fastify/websocket v11
  Non-admin user crash
  SocketStream removal
|

nonroot: |md
  **Non-Root Runtime**

  UID 1001:0 test
  Permission issues
  Delayed crash detect
  Stability monitor
|

# ── Column 5: Phase 3-5 Conditional ─────────────────
modfed: |md
  **Module Federation**

  remoteEntry.js size
  Chunk completeness
  ChunkLoadError detect
  Load performance
| {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

operator: |md
  **Operator Integration**

  Kind cluster create
  CRD install & apply
  Deployment wait
  Webhook validation
| {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

manifests: |md
  **Manifest Validation**

  Kustomize build
  ConfigMap generation
  Overlay testing
  Resource validation
| {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

# ── Column 6: Output ────────────────────────────────
generate: |md
  **Generate Workflow**

  pr-build-validation.yml
  validate-build.sh
  Test manifests
  Setup documentation
|

# ── Edges: Column 1 -> 2 ────────────────────────────
entry -> clone
clone -> detect

# ── Edges: Column 2 -> 3 (Phase 0) ──────────────────
detect -> lockfile
detect -> workspace
detect -> fips
lockfile -> preflight

# ── Edges: Column 3 -> 4 (Phase 1-2) ────────────────
preflight -> docker-build
workspace -> docker-build: context {style.stroke-dash: 3}
fips -> docker-build: flags {style.stroke-dash: 3}
docker-build -> runtime
runtime -> api-test
runtime -> ws-test
runtime -> nonroot

# ── Edges: Column 4 -> 5 (conditional phases) ───────
api-test -> modfed: "if monorepo" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
ws-test -> modfed: {style.stroke-dash: 3}
nonroot -> operator: "if operator" {style.stroke-dash: 3}
modfed -> manifests: {style.stroke-dash: 3}
operator -> manifests: {style.stroke-dash: 3}

# ── Edges: Column 5 -> 6 (output) ───────────────────
manifests -> generate: results
api-test -> generate: results {style.stroke-dash: 3}
nonroot -> generate: results {style.stroke-dash: 3}
